\f0\b ONE UNUSUAL NUANCE:
\f1\b0 \
\
The application supports various week formats.\
So if Sunday is not the first day of the week in your locale, this can now be fixed.\
\
While editing the AlarmEditor.nib file, change the repeating alarm grid to match your locale.\
Then go to "Tools" -> "Show Inspector"\
and set the tag correctly for each day of the week.\
The program will read that tag, not the position in the grid.\
The tags should be as follows:\
0: Sunday\
1: Monday\
2: Tuesday\
3: Wednesday\
4: Thursday\
5: Friday\
6: Saturday\
\
(This is how they are set in the underlying code)\
