\f0\b WINDOW TITLES:\
\

\f1\b0 The windows titles are one of the only things that may not be changed by double-clicking on the words.  These are changed in the Inspector.\
First click on the window, then go to "Tools"->"Show Inspector", and there should be a field in the Inspector called "Window Title".  The titles may be changed here.\
